    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is the right hon. and learned Gentleman aware that action has already been taken in withdrawing services from local authorities which they have hitherto satisfactorily administered with the general approval of all their citizens?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
